---
import ScrollReveal from './ScrollReveal.tsx';
---
<section class="relative py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <ScrollReveal client:visible>
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] mb-10">
        <span class="text-sm text-brand-gold font-medium">核心痛点</span>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>

    <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={100}>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8 leading-tight">
        豆包、Kimi、千问……<br />
        <span class="text-text-muted">为何总是</span><span class="gradient-text">"失忆"</span><span class="text-text-muted">？</span>
      </h2>
    </ScrollReveal>

    <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={200}>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 leading-relaxed">
        每次打开大模型 App，它都不记得你是谁、你做过什么、你喜欢什么。<br class="hidden md:block" />
        对话一旦结束，记忆就像沙滩上的脚印，被潮水冲刷得一干二净。
      </p>
    </ScrollReveal>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={300}>
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-bg-card border border-border-subtle text-left">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-brand-gold"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m15 9-6 6"/><path d="m9 9 6 6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">没有长期记忆</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">每次对话都是全新的开始，AI 记不住你的偏好、习惯和过往经历。</p>
        </div>
      </ScrollReveal>

      <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={400}>
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-bg-card border border-border-subtle text-left">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-brand-gold"><rect width="20" height="14" x="2" y="7" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">无法感知真实世界</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">AI 被困在屏幕里，不知道你今天去了哪里、见了什么人、经历了什么。</p>
        </div>
      </ScrollReveal>

      <ScrollReveal client:visible delay={500}>
        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-bg-card border border-border-subtle text-left">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-brand-gold"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">各平台记忆孤岛</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">豆包的记忆 Kimi 读不到，ChatGPT 的记忆文心一言看不到，数据互不流通。</p>
        </div>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
